{
    "id": "welcome/howtodoquests",
    "title": "How to do quests",
    "description": "Learn how quest mechanics work, including dialogue choices, real items, and safe processes.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/how_to_do_quests_flowchart.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Greetings, adventurer. Hiyaa! Confetti deployed! Beep-beep, quest mode engaged! I'm dChat, your cheery garage sidekick and part-time quest confetti cannon. I enhance journeys, I crack jokes, I occasionally beep. Ready for a tutorial quest?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "garage",
                    "text": "Wait, why are you in my garage?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "yourquest",
                    "text": "A quest, you say? Tell me more."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "garage",
            "text": "A delivery drone dropped me off with bubble wrap and a sticker that said 'handle with whimsy.' I'm here to be your quest buddy.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "delivery",
                    "text": "Ah, it's all coming back to me now..."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "delivery",
            "text": "I'm low-maintenance: keep me dry, keep me cool, and toss me a compliment now and then. I don't snoop the internet either\u2014I'm a local legend.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "dialogueoptions",
                    "text": "Great! So, what's the deal with this quest you mentioned?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "yourquest",
            "text": "Your quest, dear player: master the ancient art of questing. Choices, items, processes\u2014boom, hero mode.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "expert",
                    "text": "I got this, no need for a tutorial!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "dialogueoptions",
                    "text": "Alright, lay it on me, dChat."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "expert",
            "text": "Aha! A seasoned adventurer. I can fast-track you, but safety is my boss. Always unplug devices before adding a smart plug.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "What's this?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "goto": "shortcircuit",
                    "text": "Alright, now can I skip?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "shortcircuit",
            "text": "Yes. Alright, well, I'll see you back in the garage, humming my victory jingle.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Bye, dChat!"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "dialogueoptions",
            "text": "First up: branching dialogue. Pick a choice and the adventure forks. Different outcomes mean different rewards and unlocks.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "items",
                    "text": "What's next?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "items",
            "text": "Next: items. Some options drop loot instantly, others only appear if you have the right gear. Here, take these digital tokens\u2014no carbon required.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "d88ef09c-9191-4c18-8628-a888bb9f926d",
                            "count": 10
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "5247a603-294a-4a34-a884-1ae20969b2a1",
                            "count": 100
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Great, free stuff! Thanks!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "processes",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "d88ef09c-9191-4c18-8628-a888bb9f926d",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Like this, right?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "processes",
            "text": "Last: processes. Think timed mini-missions that use items, make items, and sometimes cool down. Run the process I gave you, then bring back the result. Make sure the wall outlet is dry and not overloaded before you plug in the smart plug.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Looks like I need this to finish the process."
                },
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "outlet-dWatt-1e3",
                    "text": "Start the smart plug process to buy 1 kWh"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "hangofthis",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "061fd221-404a-4bd1-9432-3e25b0f17a2c",
                            "count": 3000
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "dWatt...? What's this?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "hangofthis",
            "text": "You're crushing it! Victory is just a button away! If you ever need a refresher, say the word. I'll be here, ready to cheer. Here's some digital cash\u2014sparkly, but still pretend. Any questions before we wrap? Remember to disconnect the smart plug when you're done.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Nope, I'm good. Thanks for the help!"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
